                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17890422-60-off262 t17890422-60-cd263"></join>, a pair of black breeches, value 5 s. two muslin aprons, value 4 s. another apron, value 1 s. a pillow-case, value 1 s. a silk handkerchief, value 2 s. the property of 
                     
