             sworn.</p>
               <p>I saw the prisoner with the bundle under his arm, when my master caught hold of him.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17890422-60-person556">
                  JAMES
                   GRIFFITHS
               <interp inst="t17890422-60-person556" type="surname" value="GRIFFITHS"></interp>
